statements: SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols
SELECT researcher_name, research_facility FROM stem_cell_research_protocols
SELECT protocol_id, researcher_name, research_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE cell_source = 'Embryonic'
SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols ORDER BY research_date DESC
SELECT researcher_name, research_facility FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE protocol_id = 3
SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE protocol_id = 1;
SELECT researcher_name, research_facility FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE cell_source IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols ORDER BY research_date DESC;
SELECT researcher_name, research_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE research_facility = 'Lab A' ORDER BY researcher_name ASC;
SELECT protocol_id, researcher_name, research_facility FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE research_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols;
SELECT protocol_name, researcher_name, start_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE research_type = 'Clinical';
SELECT protocol_name, end_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_name, researcher_name FROM stem_cell_research_protocols ORDER BY researcher_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM compliance_reports WHERE compliance_status = 'Pending' ORDER BY submission_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE researcher_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT protocol_name, start_date, end_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE research_type = 'Clinical Trial' ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT protocol_name, researcher_name, start_date, end_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT researcher_name, COUNT(*) AS total_protocols FROM stem_cell_research_protocols GROUP BY researcher_name ORDER BY total_protocols DESC;

SELECT cr.report_id, cr.compliance_status, cr.submission_date, cr.reviewer_name, scp.protocol_name FROM compliance_reports cr JOIN stem_cell_research_protocols scp ON cr.protocol_id = scp.protocol_id WHERE cr.compliance_status = 'Approved';
SELECT * FROM stem_cell_research_protocols;
SELECT researcher_name, protocol_description FROM stem_cell_research_protocols;
SELECT protocol_id, researcher_name, protocol_date FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE researcher_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_description FROM stem_cell_research_protocols ORDER BY protocol_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM research_facilities WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM research_facilities WHERE facility_id = 1;
SELECT facility_name, contact_person FROM research_facilities WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT protocol_id, researcher_name FROM stem_cell_research_protocols ORDER BY protocol_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM compliance_checks WHERE compliance_result = TRUE ORDER BY check_date ASC;
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_description FROM stem_cell_research_protocols WHERE researcher_name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM research_protocols;
SELECT protocol_name, researcher_name FROM research_protocols;
SELECT * FROM experiments WHERE experiment_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT report_id, compliance_status FROM compliance_reports ORDER BY report_id DESC;
SELECT violation_description FROM violations WHERE violation_date BETWEEN '2021-05-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM research_protocols WHERE protocol_name = 'Example Protocol' ORDER BY protocol_id DESC;
SELECT protocol_name, researcher_name FROM research_protocols WHERE start_date < '2022-01-01';

SELECT rp.protocol_name, e.experiment_name, cr.compliance_status FROM research_protocols rp JOIN experiments e ON rp.protocol_id = e.protocol_id JOIN compliance_reports cr ON e.experiment_id = cr.experiment_id WHERE cr.report_date >= '2022-01-01' AND cr.report_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM research_protocols JOIN experiments USING (protocol_id) ORDER BY experiment_date ASC, protocol_id DESC;
SELECT v.violation_id, cr.report_id, v.violation_description FROM violations v JOIN compliance_reports cr ON v.report_id = cr.report_id ORDER BY v.violation_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM research_protocols;
SELECT protocol_name, researcher_name FROM research_protocols WHERE ethically_compliant = true;
SELECT protocol_name, researcher_name, ethically_compliant FROM research_protocols ORDER BY protocol_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM research_reviews WHERE compliance_rating > 3;
SELECT protocol_name, consent_text FROM research_protocols INNER JOIN research_consent_forms ON research_protocols.protocol_id = research_consent_forms.protocol_id;
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_name, researcher_name FROM research_protocols ORDER BY protocol_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM research_reviews WHERE compliance_rating > 3 ORDER BY review_date ASC;
SELECT r.protocol_id, r.researcher_name, c.chairperson_name FROM research_protocols r JOIN research_ethics_committee c ON r.protocol_id = c.committee_id;
SELECT rp.protocol_name, rf.consent_text FROM research_protocols rp JOIN research_consent_forms rf ON rp.protocol_id = rf.protocol_id;

SELECT ras.study_id, rp.protocol_name, rcf.consent_text FROM research_approved_studies ras JOIN research_protocols rp ON ras.protocol_id = rp.protocol_id JOIN research_consent_forms rcf ON rp.protocol_id = rcf.protocol_id ORDER BY approval_date DESC;
